<section class="section py-5">
  <div class="container">
    <div class="row">
      <div class="col-md-12">
        <h5 class="text-primary text-uppercase">What is mutual fund?</h5>
        <p>A mutual fund is a trust that pools together the savings of a number of investors who share a common financial goal. The money collected is then invested in capital market instruments such as shares, debentures and other securities.</p>
        <p>With mutual fund, you have the facility of letting professional fund managers make investments on your behalf. This means that you can have your investments professionally managed in a mutual fund. Before taking any investment decision, it is important to assess your needs and financial goals.</p>
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>
</section>

{# objectives #}
